social_posts.post_text: Considering posting more often 🪐✨ Life has been a bit chaotic but I think the dust is finally starting to settle and I’m feeling ready to be a bit more vulnerable. So naturally….bangs 💇🏻‍♀️
Back in black 🖤 I’m headed to Mexico City today for EDC weekend. 🇲🇽🎆 I hear Mexico goes pretty hard even if the fashion isn’t as crazy. Can you guess which sets are on my must-see list??? 😈

This is where all the vibes are at 💁🏻‍♀️✨

#rave #edm #goodvibesonly #edc #edcmexico #edclasvegas #ravegirl

@crssdfest, you never disappoint 🐍 On another note, it’s crazy to think that NONE of these people were my friends when I moved to SD 🤯 The way music brings people together is pretty magical and I do have the say the quality of people I’ve found are top tier 👌✨

Congrats @tessla_venus and @sunchaser97 💍 I’m so grateful the have witnessed your love story 🥹 I’m not sure if I’ve ever met two people more meant for one another 💟💜 This wedding was a spectacle of artistry and love and I’m so happy that I was able to be part of it 💐 

PS. For anyone interested, I uploaded the set I played at their wedding to my SoundCloud. Check stories or the link in my bio 💖👑 Enjoy!

📸 thanks to @leighroberts_ for the beautiful photos 😍

Hi friends, I’m playing a set tomorrow night at @avenuepb for the @bangercity.love takeover 💥I’ve been dying to play here cuz I freakin’ love this bar and I’m stoked to share the decks with these lovely people 👉 @nandito.music @arnieboyz @onica.nicole @djsunset.lit @moonlightmusic.io 🫶My set starts at 9pm tomorrow. If you’re down for some house music, come through! ❤️‍🔥🖤😘

Shoutout to all the festival boyfriends 🫶 

#crssd #crssdfest #crssdfestival #crssdfest2023 #festivalseason #festivalfashion #festivaloutfit #edmfestival

Hellloooo, I’m finally recovered from @crssdfest 🐍🐍🐍 What a weekend! 🌴😎🎶 I’ve been going to CRSSD for so long and now that I live in San Diego, I feel so spoiled having this festival basically in my backyard. I’ll definitely be back in Spring and hope to see you there! 🙌

If you enjoyed this review, lmk! Maybe I’ll make one for @dreamstateusa and @propernye 🪩 But just so you know, both Proper and Dreamstate were some of my favorite fests last year - so you should probably just go 🤪

#crssdfest #fngrscrssd #crssdfestival #edm #festivalfashion

It’s my birthday next week. Don’t ask how old I’m turning because idk…I’m just a baby 🤷🏻‍♀️

Despite some annoying self talk and identity crises, I’m grateful for a lot of the experiences I had this year. I found many meaningful moments with people I love. I hope to create more moments that bring out the best in me in the year to come. 

Anyways, enjoy these photos I never posted while feeling too many things this year 🫠 I’ll consider some late recaps posts because tbh it was hard to choose 10 photos. I have been withholding a lot 😅

But really and truly, I appreciate all the people who made this past year special 💟 Cheers to what comes next!
I reuploaded my birthday set. Sorry for the delay 😅 Happy new year 🥳💙🫶 (link in bio)

New year, same dance. You’ll always find me on the dancefloor for NYE…my happy place, surrounded by music and friends. Wouldn’t miss it 🥳🎆 Shoutout to @propernye for another amazing event. 

Favorite sets: @massanomusic, @gorgoncity, @borisbrejcha 👌
This year is starting off strong 🥳 Posting about my final day of @propernye on my last day of vacation after @afterlifetulum 😭🌴😎 Is 2024 even real 🥹 I hope so 🥰
